== About me
I'm a full-stack engineer based in Sydney. My day-to-day covers modern web stacks (React, Vue, Node, Python\/FastAPI, PostgreSQL, AWS, Docker) and a growing focus on AI-native developer tooling. I hold a Master's in Information Technology from UNSW (Excellent graduate), where my research focused on graph databases under [https://www.unsw.edu.au/staff/zhengyi-yang Zhengyi Yang]. Full background in my [CV.pdf CV].

== Education
- M.S. in Information Technology, University of New South Wales, Feb 2023 - Sep 2024 (Excellent graduate, WAM: 82/100)
- B.S. in Internet of Things, Jiangsu University of Technology, Sep 2018 - Jun 2022

#: {Award:}  “iGeek Home” WeChat Applet Contest: Third award (Oct 2019) \n “Bule Bridge Cup” Algorithm Contest: Second prize of province (April 2021)\n

== Experiences
/Golden Matrix Group Inc. Sydney, NSW, Australia ~~~~~~~~ Full Stack Software Engineer ~~~~~~~~ Apr 2025 - Present/
