- Led migration of clustered systems from traditional servers to AWS ECS containers, improving resource efficiency.
- Integrated third-party platforms (Braze, Revolut) for engagement automation and secure payment workflows.

/[https://www.aquion.com.au/ Aquion Pty Ltd] Sydney, NSW, Australia ~~~~~~~~ Software Engineer · Internship ~~~~~~~~ March 2025 - April 2025/
